metadata.name: Human Reptile
metadata.description:
The human is captured in a simulation of the reptile. A terrarium. 
The setup is a reflection of the 'between'-ness of life and the inner human nature.

It's a task of breathing with human lungs and reptile lungs at the same time.

The video work is inspired by Deleuze and Guattari's philosophical term 'becoming' (1980)

Video dimensions. 4:3

The model is the Copenhagen based bio artist Mathias Mons.
